Third-party assets bundled with FastVideoEdit
=============================================

This file lists the third-party assets vendored into this repository and their
licenses. (Python package dependencies declare their own licenses via their
distribution metadata and are not duplicated here.)

The default enrichment shipment ("auto-enrich", ENRICH_PLAN §4 Tier 0) keeps a
deliberately small third-party footprint: exactly two upstream sources — the
Noto Emoji SVG subset and the Inter font. The CTA animation pack
(vpipe/data/enrich/cta/*.webm) is our own original artwork (no third-party
emoji/CTA packs, no Lottie collections).


1. Noto Emoji  (SVG subset)
---------------------------
